    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏已正式上线！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎购买下载体验，如果遇到任何技术问题，欢迎加入我们的官方反馈群。<br>官方QQ群④【952127557】</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轻松换装</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >职业助理、星空晚礼服、沙滩泳装…多变造型由你定义！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/5bc36722c46ece40d8e91e920e742d1f.poster.avif?t=1770369377\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/5bc36722c46ece40d8e91e920e742d1f.webm?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/5bc36722c46ece40d8e91e920e742d1f.mp4?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >染色系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持发型、服饰染色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/66aa5fc4baf9a0bbd53f555ab23754d6.avif?t=1770369377\" width=1600 height=788 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人物互动</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样化的互动方式，将情感陪伴与实用功能融合，打造兼具效率工具属性与虚拟伴侣体验的桌面精灵。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基础互动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/8da04f4bf4fe7022f6f4cf740bf304aa.poster.avif?t=1770369377\" width=800 height=576 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/8da04f4bf4fe7022f6f4cf740bf304aa.webm?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/8da04f4bf4fe7022f6f4cf740bf304aa.mp4?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/517f174c90717127fc259b06e95179ba.poster.avif?t=1770369377\" width=800 height=576 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/517f174c90717127fc259b06e95179ba.webm?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/517f174c90717127fc259b06e95179ba.mp4?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >功能型互动（使用道具、实用工具）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/904c1c62ef24017a845da867a5740bc0.poster.avif?t=1770369377\" width=800 height=574 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/904c1c62ef24017a845da867a5740bc0.webm?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/904c1c62ef24017a845da867a5740bc0.mp4?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/ccecbcc8246887635047bb7d89943ffb.poster.avif?t=1770369377\" width=800 height=574 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/ccecbcc8246887635047bb7d89943ffb.webm?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/ccecbcc8246887635047bb7d89943ffb.mp4?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情任务</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式体验游戏，让你更深一层了解桌面精灵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/90a11f3f3dc5b71a894e205734dde7af.poster.avif?t=1770369377\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/90a11f3f3dc5b71a894e205734dde7af.webm?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/90a11f3f3dc5b71a894e205734dde7af.mp4?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >支持创意工坊</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以自由上传或下载Mod，让游戏内容更加丰富~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创意工坊支持添加/修改以下内容：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色模型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >服装贴图</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >文本、语音及动作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AI聊天</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/872b448cdd6494720f298566305f2cae.avif?t=1770369377\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras_big/872b448cdd6494720f298566305f2cae.avif?t=1770369377 width=800 height=454 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/c5d915a3d004c666831385492abb3c63.poster.avif?t=1770369377\" width=800 height=534 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/c5d915a3d004c666831385492abb3c63.webm?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/c5d915a3d004c666831385492abb3c63.mp4?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>戳她会有反应，对话能懂你情绪，换装展现个性——这个桌面精灵既是帮你规划任务的助手，也是懂你喜怒的贴心伙伴。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/2925a23f149f065e17ad4bcc43bfc222.avif?t=1770369377\" width=616 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
